---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="bg-brand-dark border-t border-white/5 pt-16 pb-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-12">
      <!-- Brand & Socials -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left"
      >
        <div class="text-2xl font-anton tracking-wider text-white mb-4">
          EL TÍO <span class="text-brand-neon">KIKE</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6 max-w-xs">
          La comunidad número uno de entretenimiento y casino online. Juega
          seguro, juega con Kike.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/kikeapuestas/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 hover:bg-brand-neon hover:text-black transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M12.315 2c2.43 0 2.784.013 3.808.06 1.064.049 1.791.218 2.427.465a4.902 4.902 0 011.772 1.153 4.902 4.902 0 011.153 1.772c.247.636.416 1.363.465 2.427.048 1.067.06 1.407.06 4.123v.08c0 2.643-.012 2.987-.06 4.043-.049 1.064-.218 1.791-.465 2.427a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153 1.772 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772 1.153c-.636.247-1.363.416-2.427.465-1.067.048-1.407.06-4.123.06h-.08c-2.643 0-2.987-.012-4.043-.06-1.064-.049-1.791-.218-2.427-.465a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772-1.153 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153-1.772c-.247-.636-.416-1.363-.465-2.427-.047-1.024-.06-1.379-.06-3.808v-.63c0-2.43.013-2.784.06-3.808.049-1.064.218-1.791.465-2.427a4.902 4.902 0 011.153-1.772A4.902 4.902 0 015.45 2.525c.636-.247 1.363-.416 2.427-.465C8.901 2.013 9.256 2 11.685 2h.63zm-.081 1.802h-.468c-2.456 0-2.784.011-3.807.058-.975.045-1.504.207-1.857.344-.467.182-.8.398-1.15.748-.35.35-.566.683-.748 1.15-.137.353-.3.882-.344 1.857-.047 1.023-.058 1.351-.058 3.807v.468c0 2.456.011 2.784.058 3.807.045.975.207 1.504.344 1.857.182.466.399.8.748 1.15.35.35.683.566 1.15.748.353.137.882.3 1.857.344 1.054.048 1.37.058 4.041.058h.08c2.597 0 2.917-.01 3.96-.058.976-.045 1.505-.207 1.858-.344.466-.182.8-.398 1.15-.748.35-.35.566-.683.748-1.15.137-.353.3-.882.344-1.857.048-1.055.058-1.37.058-4.041v-.08c0-2.597-.01-2.917-.058-3.96-.045-.976-.207-1.505-.344-1.858a3.097 3.097 0 00-.748-1.15 3.098 3.098 0 00-1.15-.748c-.353-.137-.882-.3-1.857-.344-1.023-.047-1.351-.058-3.807-.058zM12 6.865a5.135 5.135 0 110 10.27 5.135 5.135 0 010-10.27zm0 1.802a3.333 3.333 0 100 6.666 3.333 3.333 0 000-6.666zm5.338-3.205a1.2 1.2 0 110 2.4 1.2 1.2 0 010-2.4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
            >
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@kikeapuestas"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 hover:bg-brand-neon hover:text-black transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M19.812 5.418c.861.23 1.538.907 1.768 1.768C21.998 8.746 22 12 22 12s-.002 3.254-.42 4.814a2.504 2.504 0 0 1-1.768 1.768c-1.56.419-7.812.419-7.812.419s-6.252 0-7.812-.419a2.505 2.505 0 0 1-1.768-1.768C2 15.254 2 12 2 12s.002-3.254.42-4.814a2.507 2.507 0 0 1 1.768-1.768C5.748 5 12 5 12 5s6.252 0 7.812.418zM9.546 14.63l5.885-3.053-5.885-3.053v6.106z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
            >
          </a>
          <a
          href="https://kick.com/kickeapuestas"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 hover:bg-[#53fc18] hover:text-black transition-all duration-300"
          aria-label="Kick"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 transform scale-[0.85]"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              d="M1.333 0h8v5.333H12V2.667h2.667V0h8v8H20v2.667h-2.667v2.666H20V16h2.667v8h-8v-2.667H12v-2.666H9.333V24h-8Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
          <a
          href="https://www.facebook.com/kikeapuesta"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 hover:bg-brand-neon hover:text-black transition-all duration-300"
          aria-label="Facebook"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 transform scale-[0.90]"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left"
      >
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">
          Juego Responsable
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-brand-neon transition-colors"
              >Términos y Condiciones</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-brand-neon transition-colors"
              >Política de Privacidad</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-brand-neon transition-colors"
              >Autoexclusión</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-brand-neon transition-colors"
              >+18 Solo para mayores de edad</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Warning Warning text -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left"
      >
        <div
          class="bg-[#1a1a1a] p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 inline-block text-sm text-left relative overflow-hidden"
        >
          <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-red-500"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-medium mb-2 pl-2">
            El juego puede ser adictivo. Por favor, juega de forma responsable.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs pl-2">
            Los juegos de azar están dirigidos exclusivamente a un público
            adulto. La participación en los juegos no garantiza beneficios
            económicos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="border-t border-white/5 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center px-4 space-y-4 md:space-y-0 text-xs text-gray-600"
    >
      <p>
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Kike Apuestas. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center md:justify-end gap-2 text-center md:text-right"
      >
        <span
          >Diseñado por <a
            href="https://daviddevmx.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hover:text-brand-neon transition-colors font-semibold"
            >DEVMARSAN</a
          ></span
        >
        <span class="text-white/20 px-1">|</span>
        <span
          >Hospedado en <a
            href="https://daviddevmx.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hover:text-brand-neon transition-colors font-semibold"
            >Rock Hosting Plus</a
          ></span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
